spanGrp.span: Yís të sũã-ra-nã pe tsõ mãĩ shkablö
fighting and making a lot of things with stones and stuff.
je ñã kbö-gẽ je tsõ rö tã'ĩ jirö nẽ yowö jak wa jirö wa
Then there was one who covered his face with a piece of something.
Jekepa e-gla kajki je wö blá-wã (_) jirö taglö wa
He thought he was eating something edible;
Jekepa í të í begetsá-nã í kajki rö jirö ñõ (_) jirö ñõ-glö
he did eat it. But then he realized it was not edible,
je ñẽwã-ite jekepa í sũã-ite-ra (_) ka rö je kuna
but rather something that people use in order to burst on others.
ta pe wã jirö tsiginẽwã-glö siga-wa inga
But when he realized, somethng got stuck on his face.’
Ñerö kuando í wöjanã'-ra-nã jirö dabánãnẽ í wö inga
